column2: End Guarantee decisions activated
Ending of Guarantees
By activating this decision you can check if you can end any guarantees you might have at the moment. (NOTE: You need to leave and re-enter the Diplomacy tab for the interface to properly update!)
Ending of Guarantees
By activating this decision you can hide the End Guarantee type decisions from the interface. (NOTE: You need to leave and re-enter the Diplomacy tab for the interface to properly update!)
